      <title>伊姆兰·汗的定罪对巴基斯坦选举意味着什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-does-imran-khans-conviction-mean-pakistans-election-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前总理、板球明星伊姆兰·汗周三因非法出售国家礼品罪被判处 14 年监禁，一天前他因泄露国家机密被判处 10 年徒刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-does-imran-khans-conviction-mean-pakistans-election-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飞机出租人与俄罗斯就被困飞机达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aviation-lessor-settlements-with-russia-over-trapped-planes-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2022 年莫斯科入侵乌克兰以来，俄罗斯滞留的约 400 架飞机中，有超过四分之一的飞机租赁公司已与俄罗斯达成了总额超过 25 亿美元的和解协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aviation-lessor-settlements-with-russia-over-trapped-planes-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦选举候选人在部落地区被枪杀-警方</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-election-candidate-shot-dead-tribal-district-police-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方称，一名参加下周巴基斯坦选举的国民议会候选人周三在阿富汗边境的部落地区被枪杀，原因是担心议会投票周围的武装暴力活动加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-election-candidate-shot-dead-tribal-district-police-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界法院将对俄罗斯是否违反乌克兰国际条约做出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/world-court-rule-whether-russia-violated-international-treaties-ukraine-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国最高法院将于周三就俄罗斯资助乌克兰亲俄分裂分子（包括2014年击落马航MH17航班的分裂分子）是否违反反恐条约作出裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/world-court-rule-whether-russia-violated-international-treaties-ukraine-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 完成收购印尼顶级电子商务平台的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-completes-deal-indonesias-top-e-commerce-platform-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok已经完成了对印度尼西亚最大电子商务平台的控制权交易，这使得这家中国社交媒体巨头能够重启在该国的在线购物业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-completes-deal-indonesias-top-e-commerce-platform-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:58:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚内阁讨论赦免纳吉布，但不会宣布结果 - 部长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-cabinet-discusses-najib-pardon-bid-wont-announce-outcome-minister-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚内政部长周三表示，在对结果的疯狂猜测中，马来西亚内阁已经讨论了被监禁的前总理纳吉布·拉扎克(Najib Razak)提出的皇家赦免请求，但无权做出任何宣布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-cabinet-discusses-najib-pardon-bid-wont-announce-outcome-minister-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊姆兰·汗：针对巴基斯坦前总理的刑事案件有哪些？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/main-criminal-cases-against-pakistans-imran-khan-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗和他的妻子布什拉·汗因涉嫌非法出售国家礼品而被分别判处 14 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/main-criminal-cases-against-pakistans-imran-khan-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:12:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台军模拟中国将演习变成攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-military-simulates-china-turning-drills-into-an-attack-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾军方周三模拟了中国突然将其一次环岛定期演习转变为实际攻击的场景，同一天中国在台湾附近进行了另一次“战备巡逻”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-military-simulates-china-turning-drills-into-an-attack-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:37:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾芯片制造商联电今年谨慎乐观，资本支出增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwan-chipmaker-umc-cautiously-optimistic-this-year-ups-capex-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾芯片制造商联华电子 (UMC) 周三表示，即使宏观经济存在不确定性，该公司对今年的需求仍持“谨慎乐观”态度，因为该公司的资本支出较 2023 年增加了 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwan-chipmaker-umc-cautiously-optimistic-this-year-ups-capex-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:37:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼首席安全部长即将辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-chief-security-minister-tender-resignation-soon-2024-01-31/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚首席安全部长兼副总统候选人马福德周三表示，他将提出辞职，他的助手表示，这一决定是由于总统佐科维多多在下个月的选举中选边站队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-chief-security-minister-tender-resignation-soon-2024-01-31/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
